{
  "texts": [
    "The personalized responses from ChatGPT serve as language from the \"more knowledgeable other,\" providing the necessary support to help the learner move forward.",
    "Vygotsky emphasized the importance of social context and interaction in learning, and by customizing responses, ChatGPT is essentially adapting the learning process to fit the social and cultural context of the learner.",
    "The 2 nd level is prompting and providing answers based on timely learning.",
    "This is an example of scaffolding within the ZPD, where support is provided in a paced and step-by-step way to give just enough assistance to move the learner forward.",
    "By providing prompts or answers in a timely manner, ChatGPT helps to maintain the learner's engagement and motivation, gradually reducing the level of support as the learner becomes more capable."
  ]
}